title: 4 Jewish Cooking ebooks Roden Marks Silver Kancigor
description:
Title 1:

Knish: In Search of the Jewish Soul Food (HBI Series on Jewish Women) by Laura Silver



Title 2:

Encyclopedia of Jewish Food by Gil Marks



Title 3:

The Book of Jewish Food: An Odyssey from Samarkand to New York by Claudia Roden



Title 4:

The Perfect Passover Cookbook: Family-Tested Recipes for Matzoh Ball Soup, Kugel, Haroset, and More, Plus 25 Desserts by Judy Bart Kancigor



Note: Had a quick look through these four books in both file types using Calibre for PC for the epub files, and Kindle for PC for the mobi.

Enjoy.
